text: Alla Mikayelyan (born 19 December 1969) is an Armenian cross-country skier. She competed in the women's 30 kilometre freestyle at the 1998 Winter Olympics. ==References== Category:1969 births Category:Living people Category:Armenian female cross-country skiers Category:Olympic cross-country skiers of Armenia Category:Cross-country skiers at the 1998 Winter Olympics Category:People from Ararat Province
